== 权力移交与解散 ==
2012年8月8日，全国过渡委员会正式将权力移交给[[利比亚国民议会|利比亚国民议会]]，国民议会成为利比亚的最高权力机构。全国过渡委员会当天也正式解散<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/news/world/middle-east/2012/08/08/libya-transitional-rulers-hand-over-power/uMPkXd9vTSSHg589mU9ykJ/story.html |title=Libya's transitional rulers hand over power |author=Esam Mohamed |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date=8 August 2012 |publisher=Boston.com |accessdate=8 August 2012 |archive-date=2012-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121208121751/http://www.boston.com/news/world/middle-east/2012/08/08/libya-transitional-rulers-hand-over-power/uMPkXd9vTSSHg589mU9ykJ/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

